snippet.title: HotBunz Announcement Trailer (Steam)
snippet.description:
Hot Bunz is a physics-based 2D Platformer Party Game with one goal - players must navigate their characters through an obstacle course with rotating rings to collect as many gold coins in a series of increasingly complex level

Wishlist here https://store.steampowered.com/app/2229230/HotBunz/
